@NODE "Requirements" "Requirements..."

@{b}     REQUIREMENTS@{ub}

     ·    any AMIGA computer
     ·    monitor or TV (color is the best)
     ·    mouse
     ·    Kickstart 1.3 or higher
     ·    At least 1MB of free memory
     ·    2.5 MB of space on your hard disc
@ENDNODE

